# §C — v0.1.60 SCOPE — Multi-vote Giant + Deep Test 14-domain + Full Plow Loop demonstrable + LB membership + Stage 6 + Post Results + Cue Deck Card share

**Theme:** the FULL substrate-accumulator architecture demonstrable end-to-end. v0.1.60 is the version the Founder velocity statement targets ("AS SOON AS POSSIBLE to v0.1.60"). This is where the moat goes from "buildable" to "built."

## SEG-1 · Multi-vote Giant concordance (P0, **Sonnet 4.6**)

**Goal:** scale concordance from 3 voters (v0.1.58) to configurable N (default 5+) with weighted voting + perspective-diverse prompts (correctness / consistency / coverage / security / repro).

**Scope:**
- Extend `giant_concordance.ts` from v0.1.58
- Voter pool: 5+ parallel Gemma calls with 5+ distinct perspective-lens prompts (per Bishop's adversarial-verify canon — "diversity catches failure modes redundancy can't")
- Weighted voting: high-confidence verdicts count more; ties broken by adversarial-pass lens
- Configurable threshold (3-of-5 default, 4-of-5 for high-stakes domains)
- Audit trail: every vote logged with prompt-lens + verdict + reasoning excerpt

**Verify:** seed 10 known-correct + 10 known-incorrect answers; confirm concordance discriminates ≥90% correctly.

## SEG-2 · Deep Test 14-domain tab unlock (P0, **Sonnet 4.6**)

